(24, 'about.content', '{\"has_image\":\"1\",\"heading\":\"Revolutionizing Travel in Pakistan\",\"short_description\":\"<div class=\\\"section-header\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:20px;color:rgb(119,119,119);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;\\\"><p><br \\/><\\/p><p>At Bus Reservation Web App, we are dedicated to making bus travel more accessible, convenient, and efficient for passengers across Pakistan. With our easy-to-use platform, travelers can quickly book their tickets, track buses, and enjoy a seamless journey experience.<\\/p><\\/div>\",\"title\":\"About Us\",\"description\":\"<div class=\\\"item\\\" style=\\\"margin-bottom:30px;color:rgb(119,119,119);font-family:Lato, sans-serif;\\\"><p><span style=\\\"font-size:0.875rem;\\\">Welcome to Bus Reservation Web App, the premier online platform designed to simplify bus travel across Pakistan. We offer a modern, user-friendly solution for travelers who want to book bus tickets quickly and efficiently.<\\/span><\\/p><p>Our mission is to provide a hassle-free booking experience with real-time updates, secure payment options, and a wide range of routes to choose from. Whether you\\u2019re planning a short trip or a long journey, TICKME is your trusted travel companion.<\\/p><p>We collaborate with a network of top bus operators to ensure that you have access to comfortable and reliable transportation, with features that include:<\\/p><ul><li><strong>Easy Online Booking<\\/strong>: Choose your route, select your seat, and book your ticket in minutes.<\\/li><li><strong>Secure Payment<\\/strong>: Multiple payment methods to ensure your transactions are safe.<\\/li><li><strong>Real-Time Tracking<\\/strong>: Stay informed about your bus\\u2019s location and schedule updates.<\\/li><li><strong>24\\/7 Customer Support<\\/strong>: Our team is here to assist you with any questions or issues at any time.<\\/li><\\/ul><p>At, we believe in transforming the way people travel. With a focus on convenience, safety, and customer sa<span style